Card Connect brings this action against Defendants to recover damages
and to obtain injunctive relief to prevent Defendants from further (i) misappropriating Card
Connect’s trade secrets and confidential information, (ii) soliciting Card Connect’s employees,
(iii) unfairly competing against Card Connect, and (iv) interfering with Card Connect’s
advantageous contractual relationships.
